Package: autoscroll-x11
Version: 0.1.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Joseph Wiley <flux.abyss@proton.me>
Installed-Size: 104
Depends: python3, python3-gi, python3-xlib, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/jwiley/autoscroll-x11
Description: Windows-like middle-click autoscroll for X11
 Activates smooth autoscroll when the middle mouse button is held.
 Moving away from the click position scrolls the active window in that
 direction. Releasing the button stops scrolling; a quick press and
 release is forwarded as a normal middle click.
 .
 A tray icon provides an enabled/disabled toggle and quit action.
